summary: adds a small farmhouse just outside Riverwood on the way to Whiterun. It\'s top features are it\'s location a small potato patch and a hand designed loft in the interior. It also features the Heritage bow, a powerful weapon to start the game with.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome home to the Family farmhouse. Left to you from your relatives (or the current abode of your relatives, just add some npc\'s in the editor) this house boasts many homely features. these include,

potato patch out front
location just outside Riverwood, and not far from Whiterun
wood chopping block
Fishing rack at the river
cooking pot 
safe storage
a hand designed loft upstairs

To install just download the file and unzip into your skyrim data folder. enjoy.
author: Leemcky
